Using Peaks is as easy as pie
Sampling
Whenever an event happens, send a POST request to your personal Peaks instance.
Updating 
fetch("https://peaks.bandits.deta.app/public/experiments/update", {
                                method: "POST",
                                body: JSON.stringify({
                                    key: "x1",
                                    arm_name: "red",
                                    outcome: 1,
                                }),
                                headers: {
                                    "Content-Type": "application/json",
                                },
                            });
Analyzing
Your Peaks instance will handle the rest, automatically adjusting ‘arm’ probabilities with each API call.
